#| "so configured.</P><P>The windows that are being displayed would then "
#| "transmit their data across the network. If that network is not fully "
#| "trusted, then the network traffic can be eavesdropped by an attacker, "
#| "gaining access not only to the graphical content of the display, but also "
#| "to usernames and passwords that are being used.</P><P>If you don't need "
#| "<EM>XDMCP</EM> for remote graphical logins then disable this option.</P>"
