#| msgid ""
#| "<P>If a package containing a service that is currently running is being "
#| "uninstalled, then the service is stopped before the files of the package "
#| "are removed.</P><P>This makes sense in most cases, and it is safe to do, "
#| "considering that many services either need their binaries accessible in "
